name: Omdb-search
tagline: A Polymer custom element that fetches movie, series, episode data from the Open Movie Database (OMDb) api.
body:
### Authors and Contributors
Created by Giovanni Orlando Rivera [@giovanni0918](https://github.com/giovanni0918) on July 2016 using Polymer and the Open Movie Database OMDb API.

Disclaimer: I do not own any of the data being fetched from the OMDb API, I am just an user/donor.

### Support or Contact
Having trouble using omdb-search web-component with your application? Check out our documentation for more info.
